description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Gaston purrs with a rating of 70, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 70, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 5 for East, 1 for South, and Leverage for West. Gaston has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/60701-65160-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Gaston [70 Votes, Top 9% Rating]
